{"tid":1935752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支共官方收回訓誡 重申李文亮發不實訊息","createTime":"2020-03-20T19:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T03:17:40.000Z","uid":35432,"like":197,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c0137f99c79f420b217a01b37ec3e92fe4e2a1c2","tid":1935752,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T19:02:36.000Z","msg":"早揭發支那武漢肺炎疫情8名「吹哨人」之一、2月初染疫病逝的武漢醫生李文亮，生前被官方指「散布謠言」，惹社會大為憤慨，國家監察委員會調查組調查逾月後昨公布結果，強調李文亮1月面對警方訓誡時承認未經核實就在微信群組發布「有沙士」的消息，但警方執法程序亦不規範，出具訓誡書屬不當，應予撤銷。武漢市公安局照做，並向李文亮家屬公開道歉。<br />\n<br />\n國家監委負責人提到，李文亮雖非故意擾亂公共秩序，但確是在引發疫情的病毒尚未證實之時，就轉發與實際情況不符的訊息，而且李文亮是黨員，非所謂「反體制人物」，有敵對勢力為攻擊黨和政府，標籤李文亮為「英雄」、「覺醒者」，想挑動社會情緒，「註定不會得逞」。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%94%B6%E5%9B%9E%E8%A8%93%E8%AA%A1-%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E6%9D%8E%E6%96%87%E4%BA%AE%E7%99%BC%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%A6%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF-212173?fbclid=IwAR3uek-n4mxq5R7qRtZO5lTgsJVrcnZM20WGxcmeNR0ckfuj9swfZQdKh1U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%259B%259E%25E8%25A8%2593%25E8%25AA%25A1-%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2594%25B3%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%2596%2587%25E4%25BA%25AE%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2581%25AF-212173%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3uek-n4mxq5R7qRtZO5lTgsJVrcnZM20WGxcmeNR0ckfuj9swfZQdKh1U&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXPMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=6f3eba07\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%94%B6%E5%9B%9E%E8%A8%93%E8%AA%A1-%E9%87%8D%E7%94%B3%E6%9D%8E%E6%96%87%E4%BA%AE%E7%99%BC%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%A6%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF-212173?fbclid=IwAR3uek-n4mxq5R7qRtZO5lTgsJVrcnZM20WGxcmeNR0ckfuj9swfZQdKh1U</a>"},{"pid":"bc6f65b5e92bcb9b1375ff3bb06d335a75df69bf","tid":1935752,"uid":97240,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T19:04:29.000Z","msg":"習:殺佢全家yeah<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" clas